 # ENGLISH VERSION

 # StudentFlow

 ## Description 
 StudentFlow is a student and monthly payment management system. It allows you register students, automatically generate monthly fess, and track payments efficiently.

 ## Features 

  - Student registration

  - Automatic monthly fee generation

  - payment tracking

  - Pending and paid status management

  ## Technologies

   - JavaScript

   - Node.js

   - Html

   - Css

   ## How to run

   npm install

   node server.js

   ## Author 

   Alisson7-dev